message:
Received this one pre-cleaned by another company and it actually worked when I got it. After doing some touch up work, returned it to the customer. It didn't work when the customer tested it and now that I've got it back, is doesn't work either. The fan spins, but I get no chime...

All voltages are present (CPU voltage 1.75, don't these normally measure 1.8?);
Tested another BIOS; 
Replaced clock chip;
JTAG removed;
SMC replaced;
Some touch up work. 

Any brilliant ideas?
